[
  "Former race car driver Roger Penske is the founder, chairman and CEO of publicly-traded car and truck dealer Penske Automotive Group.",
  "The business is best known for its auto dealerships, which sell new and used cars, and its iconic yellow rental trucks.",
  "Penske started his career with one car dealership in 1965, opened with a $75,000 loan from his father.",
  "In June 2019, President Trump announced that Penske will be awarded a Presidential Medal of Freedom, the highest civilian award in the U.S."
]